OL,3,CMan charged with death by dangerous
OL,4,Cdriving after newborn baby died
OL,6,FDetectives have charged two people
OL,7,Fafter a crash left a baby boy dead and
OL,8,Fhis mother seriously injured.
OL,10,FPolice and paramedics were called to
OL,11,FStation Road in Bamber Bridge, close
OL,12,Fto the junction with Longbrook Avenue
OL,13,Fand Fourfields, shortly before 8pm on
OL,14,FSeptember 29 2024.
OL,16,FThe victim, a woman in her thirties
OL,17,Ffrom Bamber Bridge, was on the
OL,18,Fpedestrian crossing when she was
OL,19,Fstruck by a car driving towards
OL,20,FPreston.
