OL,6,FA 16-year-old boy, also from Walton le
OL,7,FDale has been charged with assisting
OL,8,Fan offender. He cannot be named for
OL,9,Flegal reasons.
OL,11,FThey have both been remanded to appear
OL,12,Fbefore Preston Magistrates' Court
OL,13,Ftoday.
OL,15,FA number of other people arrested in
OL,16,Fconnection with the investigation
OL,17,Fremain on police bail.
